message: "If you use this skill, please cite it as below."
title: "GitHub for Research — a Claude Code skill"
abstract: >-
  A Claude Code skill that teaches research-grade GitHub practice to
  researchers without a software background: attribution, issues, branches,
  the GitHub Flow work cycle, data-integrity checks, reproducible
  environments, and a project history that reads like a lab notebook.
